</style>

<div class="container">
  <!-- Main hero unit for a primary marketing message or call to action -->
  <div class="hero-unit">
    <h2>About Us</h2>
    <p>Sportshoppe is a web application that aims for convenient searching and purchasing of products for patrons. Sportshoppe's main goal is to promote local sport shops that have excellent services but could not afford to advertise their greatness.</p>
  </div>

  <!-- Example row of columns -->
  <div class="row">
    <div class="span4">
      <%=link_to image_tag("search.jpg")%>
      <h2>Search</h2>
      <p>Search for your favorite shop or a product that will satisfy your needs. Searching is made more sophisticated through filtering options. </p>
    </div>
    <div class="span4">
      <%=link_to image_tag("buy.jpg")%>
      <h2>Buy</h2>
      <p>Not sure where to spend all that money? Try buying in Sportshoppe. Sign up for a patron account and get started on spending your money for quality products. </p> 
   </div>
    <div class="span4">
      <%=link_to image_tag("sell.jpg")%>
      <h2>Sell</h2>
      <p>Start up a business that will change your life. Sportshoppe offers an account for shops. Raise your popularity and gain patrons for free.</p>
    </div>
 </div>
